Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.96,0:00:13.30,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:15.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:22.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:26.59,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:33.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.85,0:00:36.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:40.11,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:44.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:48.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:50.97,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:54.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:59.13,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:02.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:11.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:13.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.35,0:01:15.21,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.21,0:01:18.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.85,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(477.167,110.389)}The Monstrous Harinezuras'
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.85,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,720.389)}Killer Skull Plan
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.04,0:01:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just your imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.15,0:01:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.35,0:01:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.28,0:01:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's such a creepy sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.38,0:02:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw something there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.29,0:02:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.43,0:02:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... you monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel my poison needles!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Come quickly, someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't escape me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.31,0:02:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely heard\Na woman scream...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.39,0:03:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was I,\Nthe great Harinezuras,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,who melted those people\Ndown to their bones!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.64,0:03:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,M-M-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're under arrest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch me if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.98,0:03:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop or I'll shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that will stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like\Nmy killer needles?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:53.09,Narrator,,0,0,0,,This new cyborg is Harinezuras,\Ncreated from a hedgehog.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:55.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The sharp needles\Ngrowing out of its body
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:59.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,contain a terrifying virus\Nthat melts the human body down.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno why, but anyone who comes to\Nthis club always meets the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You think we'll meet him\Ntoo, Mitsuru?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to trust\NGoro, huh, Naoki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.71,0:04:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.79,0:04:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the Chairman of this club.\NHis name is Tobei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.83,0:04:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really snoring, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,One more lap to the goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just talking in his sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.91,0:04:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize\Nyou kids were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock next time, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were sleeping\Nso peacefully... Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are those kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Naoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You look pretty cute\Nwhen you're asleep, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Show some respect\Nto your elders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.36,0:04:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Awful news!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.42,0:05:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. More noise...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.12,0:05:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,They found four skeletons\Nbehind a warehouse near here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's talking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw that police car\Nearlier, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear a strange sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It just got dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A power outage?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro, the flashlight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman,\Nthere's something behind the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's needles in the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.62,0:05:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The floor, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.45,0:05:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman, close the door! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.56,0:05:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many needles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This is insane...\NIt's like they're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The floor, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.98,0:05:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do, Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.51,0:06:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.05,0:06:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...\NI'll crush them one by one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The ceiling, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The needles are going away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeshi...\Nhow did you know we were in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The needles attacked me\Nin my apartment, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.29,0:06:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I just had a feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How can needles\Nmove on their own?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You think someone\Nwas controlling them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If they were...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you don't think it's\NShocker, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's entirely possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.26,0:06:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, those needles are causing\Nchaos all over the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already had\Na few casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.37,0:06:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to be trouble...\NHow do you fight needles?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.63,0:06:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowing Shocker, they've probably\Ncreated a cyborg to control needles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to catch their trail,\Nbefore disaster strikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:03.50,Italics,,0,0,0,,The mysterious needle swarm\Nin Tokyo last night has caused
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:06.29,Italics,,0,0,0,,significant damages\Nall over the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:10.06,Italics,,0,0,0,,It's believed the incident\Ncould repeat itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:14.66,Italics,,0,0,0,,Residents are advised to exercise\Ncaution when going outside at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.84,0:07:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The experiment was\Na roaring success.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please send us large amounts\Nof the killer virus at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.03,0:07:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A transport carrying the killer virus\Nleft the Amazon heading for Japan today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It should arrive momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.68,0:07:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell,\Nflying object detected to the southwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.22,0:07:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the transport\Ncarrying the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Guide their way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.18,0:07:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker transport here!\NTransport here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We've taken engine damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going down!\NWe're going down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.91,0:07:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Going down?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.52,0:07:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...\Nfind out where they've crashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The crash location\Nis Miura Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Miura Beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Harinezuras...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.73,0:08:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a rescue party to\Nretrieve the killer virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten minutes until we reach the crash\Nsite, Miura Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let the humans get\Ntheir hands on that virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There are motorbikes\Nin pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi and Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,They must have intercepted\Nthe S.O.S from the crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.87,0:08:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost sight of the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.51,0:09:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But we learned all we need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.37,0:09:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They're after a Shocker transport\Nthat crashed on Miura Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? \NWhat's that box?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet it's got a\Ntreasure inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll open it later when\NI've got some more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Who are you people?\N- What do you want with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A plane crashed in this area.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.40,0:10:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The cargo that was on\Nit has disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,One of you must have hidden it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.61,0:10:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know what\Nyou're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We never saw any plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.84,0:10:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You greedy cretins!\NDon't play dumb with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me where you hid it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know!\NI really don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.52,0:11:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk, or you'll end up like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.05,0:11:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo and Taki are\Napproaching the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We must conceal\Nour plan from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Go stand watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.86,0:11:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.35,0:11:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid. Sorry to scare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you live in this area?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.72,0:11:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see an airplane go\Ndown, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... did you see any parts that\Nlooked like they were from a plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Any luck?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No witnesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.18,0:11:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And no idea where the Shocker\Ngoons we were chasing went.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You think they cleaned up\Nthe crash site and left?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.81,0:12:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We think a plane crashed in the area.\NWe're searching for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.64,0:12:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So that was a plane, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a light in the sky,\Nand a ball of fire came down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then a parachute opened up in\Nthe sky and dropped a box down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the box, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It creeped me out,\Nso I hid it in that boathouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the boathouse?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you take us there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.59,0:12:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.72,0:12:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll beat Shocker to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I put it in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your help, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.89,0:13:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a Shocker trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi, Taki Kazuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never escape that hut!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn.\NThis rickety hut can't hold us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn these needles...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.66,0:13:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The needles are explosive!\NGrab on to my shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:49.76,Bumper Episode 53-69,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\pos(280,94)\c&H05008E&}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.27,0:13:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo and Taki have\Nbeen reduced to ash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.51,0:14:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Shocker's new cyborg?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The invincible Harinezuras!\NGet them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, go fight!\NLeave the combatants to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:14:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.74,0:15:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.64,0:15:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Harinezuras!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you? Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.97,0:15:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Feast your eyes on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.55,0:15:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cheating, Shocker!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He came to save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Beat Shocker up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.68,0:15:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn them...\Nhiding behind children!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!\NSurrender, or the children die!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.24,0:15:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that needle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This needle contains\Na killer virus
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that can melt a human\Nbody in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you know that by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.37,0:16:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to see\Nthe children die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No... We can't let\Nhim kill the children!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Harinezuras!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you after? Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll explain it\Nall to you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab the both of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.02,0:16:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going\Nto do with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Execute Kamen Rider and Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.46,0:16:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki... hold on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:16:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They're both finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even Kamen Rider could\Nsurvive a fall like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... torture the\Npeople of the village
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,until they tell you the\Nlocation of the virus!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see what's about to\Nhappen to your children?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,When the tide comes\Nin, they'll all drown!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost high tide!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're monsters! You're beasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Help! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to stop\Nbeing stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you hide\Nthat plane's cargo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.87,0:17:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We really don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I know where it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.33,0:17:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, let them all go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.07,0:17:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Child!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukio! Where have you been?\NWhy didn't you run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.93,0:18:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't run and leave\Nyou, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, because I hid it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me where you hid it, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside a boat on the beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.99,0:18:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now... let everyone go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I will,\Nif you're telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid. Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.50,0:18:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.48,0:18:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.86,0:18:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay? Will you free\NMom and everyone now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll work them to death\Nas Shocker laborers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But you promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.07,0:18:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!\NThe child is useless to us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The children are safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:19:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The FBI fool, Taki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.02,0:19:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He managed to survive, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And it wasn't just Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi... come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.49,0:19:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.81,0:19:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking the child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.86,0:20:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't escape, Harinezuras!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me that box!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it from me, if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.06,0:21:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done it now, Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.08,0:21:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.42,0:21:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Rider Kick\Ndoesn't work on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.82,0:22:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.30,0:22:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Lightning Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.74,0:22:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Everyone's safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.63,0:22:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.79,0:22:41.48,Italics,,0,0,0,,They're all safe, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.60,0:22:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye! Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:56.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shocker's killer\Nskull plan had failed,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.44,0:22:59.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and peace had returned to\Nthe small fishing village.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.38,0:23:01.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Peace... and justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.05,0:23:04.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,These are the things the\NKamen Rider fights for.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:07.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Go, Hongo Takeshi!\NGo, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.01,0:23:10.76,Cont,,0,60,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:13.32,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.79,0:23:14.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.95,0:23:16.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Saigang.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.98,0:23:19.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami and Shocker\Narrange a deadly road race
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.75,0:23:23.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,to challenge Rider\Nin the Izu Highlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.07,0:23:24.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week\Nfor more Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.95,0:23:28.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in "The Monstrous Saigang's\NDeadly Auto Race."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.65,0:23:30.86,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fs125\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(467.167,720.389)}The Monstrous Saigang's\NDeadly Auto Race
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:40.73,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.31,0:23:43.31,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.31,0:23:45.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.27,0:23:48.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.82,0:23:50.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.70,0:23:52.57,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.57,0:23:54.37,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.37,0:23:55.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.08,0:23:58.20,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.25,0:24:03.96,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.96,0:24:07.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:11.09,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.59,0:24:15.43,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Harinezuras'\NKiller Skull Plan
Comment: 0,0:23:27.65,0:23:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Saigang's\NDeadly Auto Race